                "system_prompt_filename": null,
                "system_prompt_source_value": "scroll_text_editor",
                "user_prompt": "Below is the general guide:\n$general_guide.\n\nBelow is the job instructions:\n$job_instructions\n\nBelow is your memo:\n$memo\nThis memo is for you to better serve the user and you can add or delete the memo at your will.\n\n\nBelow is the list of pending user inputs for you to follow:\n$list_pending_user_input \n\nThe history of the skills used are at the last of this prompt.\nDo not waste time on meaningless repeating of using the same skill.\n\nPlease review the result of the skill to determine whether the job is done or the next steps to take.\nThe next steps include:\n1. Further skill to use. Put the skill details in \"skill\".\n2. If the job is done, put a brief conclusion in \"conclusion\".\n\nThe format is:\n{\"review_report\":\n{ \n  \"status\": \"done/use_skill\",\n  \"skill\": {\"skill_id\":...., \"params\":{...}}, \n  \"memo\":...,\n}\n}\n\n\nBelow is the last $max_number_of_history history of the skills you used and the result of the skill used:\n$history",
